Write the setUKnotVector method in the NurbsSurface class.
Remember to respond with a snippet in the form of the following:
```
class NurbsSurface {
    setUKnotVector(uKnotVector) {
        // your code here
    }
}
```

```javascript
class NurbsSurface {
    constructor() {
        this.uknotVector = [];
    }

    setUKnotVector(uKnotVector) {
        if (!Array.isArray(uKnotVector)) {
            throw new Error('Input must be an array');
        }

        this.uknotVector = uKnotVector;
    }
}
```
